
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Crypto Concierge Marbella</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600&family=Playfair+Display:wght@500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    html, body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #f9f6ef, #e9dfd2);
      color: #2b2b2b;
    }

    main {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 8rem 1.5rem 6rem;
      min-height: 100vh;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .logo {
      width: 140px;
      height: auto;
      margin-bottom: 2.2rem;
      display: block;
    }

    .tagline {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.7rem;
      max-width: 620px;
      margin: 0 auto 3rem;
      color: #3a3a3a;
    }

    .cta-button {
      background: #1a1a1a;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 1.1rem 2.2rem;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
      background: #333;
    }

    .section {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 2.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
      padding-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      line-height: 2;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      text-align: justify;
    }

    strong {
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    footer {
      background: #f1ede4;
      color: #888;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
      margin-top: 4rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main>
    <img src="logo_transparent_final.png" alt="Crypto Concierge Marbella Logo" class="logo" />
    <p class="tagline">Discreet crypto onboarding for high-net-worth individuals, expats, and digital asset holders in Spain’s luxury capital.</p>
    <a class="cta-button" href="mailto:ccmarbella@proton.me">Request Consultation</a>
  </main>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>What We Do</h2>
    <p><strong>Cold Wallet Setup:</strong> Bespoke wallet installs, secure backup design, and vault-grade storage. In-person and discreet.</p>
    <p><strong>Private Crypto Consultations:</strong> One-on-one strategy sessions focused on privacy, jurisdictional awareness, and multisig security.</p>
    <p><strong>OTC Desk Introductions:</strong> Tap into reliable high-volume OTC desks for confidential trades.</p>
    <p><strong>ATM Integrations:</strong> We help onboard and place compliant crypto ATMs in exclusive Marbella venues.</p>
    <p>All services are conducted in strict privacy. No custodial holding. Every consultation is by request only.</p>
  </div>

  <footer>
    &copy; 2025 Crypto Concierge Marbella — All rights reserved.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
